{"tid":2166231,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"政府延長現有電動車首次登記稅寬減安排3年","createTime":"2020-08-20T09:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T02:58:00.000Z","uid":64603,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"97b0b9eb695678d474c34137f4c76b636df9c96b","tid":2166231,"uid":64603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:56:46.000Z","msg":"政府延長電動車首次登記稅現有寬減安排的期限3年，至2024年3月31日。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，電動車首次登記稅的現有寬減安排原訂於2021年3月31日完結，經檢視市場情況及電動車發展等因素後，決定延長期限3年，有助業界引入電動車的供應數量和型號，市民亦可享有合適的環保選擇，共同支持綠色復蘇。<br />\n<br />\n另外，今年預算案提出制定本港首份電動車普及化路線圖，預期在2021年首季完成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544920-20200820.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544920-20200820.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5RjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=d3b7e003\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544920-20200820.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fefb1c7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544920-20200820.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7ff23d8a81977e8a240e7ce2705e79a06d6626f5","tid":2166231,"uid":23160,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"免稅啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"923459465b861e7c00f2292e114d7a9368a5e5e6","tid":2166231,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:06:25.000Z","msg":"恒馳"},{"pid":"23f485a0d595c8e232985b2af5982ee462147cf5","tid":2166231,"uid":54095,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"恆馳 123456 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e076752a97d116a0a514ca4014b8820d392572d","tid":2166231,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2